<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Data Entry Job</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 text-white font-sans">

  
  <header class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 bg-gray-800">
    <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">
      <a href="/">SkillSphere</a>
    </div>
    <nav class="flex space-x-6 text-sm">
      <a href="new.ejs" class="hover:text-pink-400">Home</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-pink-500 mb-4">Data Entry Specialist</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
      <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt mr-1"></i> On-site | 
      <i class="far fa-clock mx-1"></i> Part-Time | 
      <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave mx-1"></i> ₹15,000 - ₹25,000 INR/month
    </p>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-pink-400">Job Description</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300">
        We're looking for a reliable Data Entry Specialist to input and manage data in our systems. This is a great opportunity for students or part-time professionals looking to earn from home or office.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-pink-400">Responsibilities</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-1">
        <li>Enter accurate data into spreadsheets, forms, and databases.</li>
        <li>Verify and cross-check information for errors.</li>
        <li>Organize and maintain records with confidentiality.</li>
        <li>Generate reports as needed by the supervisor.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-pink-400">Qualifications</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-1">
        <li>Basic computer literacy and typing speed of 40+ WPM.</li>
        <li>Attention to detail and ability to multitask.</li>
        <li>Prior experience in data entry is preferred but not required.</li>
        <li>Familiarity with MS Excel or Google Sheets is a plus.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-pink-400">Apply Now</h2>
      <form id="applyForm" class="space-y-4">
        <input type="text" class="w-full p-3 bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded" id="fname" placeholder="Your Name" required>
        <input type="email" class="w-full p-3 bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded" id="f-email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
        <input type="text" class="w-full p-3 bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded" id="f-portfolio" placeholder="Portfolio URL (Optional)">
        <textarea class="w-full p-3 bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded" rows="5" id="f-cover" placeholder="Cover Letter"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700 font-bold py-3 rounded">Submit Application</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-center text-gray-400 text-sm py-6">
    © 2025 SkillSphere. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById("applyForm").addEventListener("submit", function (e) {
      e.preventDefault();

      const data = {
        name: document.getElementById("fname").value,
        email: document.getElementById("f-email").value,
        portfolio: document.getElementById("f-portfolio").value,
        cover: document.getElementById("f-cover").value
      };

      fetch("http://localhost:8000/saveData", {
        method: "POST",
        headers: {
          "Content-Type": "application/json"
        },
        body: JSON.stringify(data)
      })
      .then(res => res.text())
      .then(data => alert("Application submitted successfully!"))
      .catch(err => alert("There was an error submitting your application."));
    });
  </script>
</body>
</
